00:07:45.330 --> 00:07:49.850 align:middle line:90%
Exploration" in 1994.

00:07:49.850 --> 00:07:54.160 align:middle line:84%
It begins with human
DNA once again.

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:57.770 align:middle line:84%
And this is a very
precise kind of human DNA.

00:07:57.770 --> 00:08:02.510 align:middle line:84%
It comes from umbilical
cords of newborns,

00:08:02.510 --> 00:08:07.670 align:middle line:84%
