00:08:12.250 --> 00:08:15.470 align:middle line:84%
So it's a very
pristine kind of DNA.

00:08:15.470 --> 00:08:19.650 align:middle line:84%
And the DNA is
isolated in one vessel,

00:08:19.650 --> 00:08:21.800 align:middle line:84%
and that is encased
in another vessel

00:08:21.800 --> 00:08:24.830 align:middle line:84%
to make sure that there are
no other influences that

00:08:24.830 --> 00:08:29.750 align:middle line:84%
are happening from outside
