00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:28.860 align:middle line:84%
Under another set
of circumstances,

00:19:28.860 --> 00:19:31.510 align:middle line:90%
the particles became waves.

00:19:31.510 --> 00:19:34.120 align:middle line:84%
So now we're
talking on a quantum

00:19:34.120 --> 00:19:36.880 align:middle line:84%
level about the difference
between the particles

00:19:36.880 --> 00:19:37.900 align:middle line:90%
and waves.

00:19:37.900 --> 00:19:41.930 align:middle line:84%
It's the same energy expressing
